		reference_id: '6',
		content: "# Onepoint recognised as one of the UK's Top 40 SMEs\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  "LONDON, UNITED KINGDOM- 21, March 2026 – Onepoint, the award-winning AI and technology consultancy, has been named as one of the UK's leading small and medium-sized enterprises.\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  "The Elite Business Top 100 SMEs (EB100) National Awards, hosted by Elite Business Magazine, celebrate the UK's most exceptional SME businesses. The award recognises organisations that demonstrate strategic leadership, innovation, resilience, and long-term impact. Among hundreds of entries across diverse sectors, Onepoint was ranked 37th.\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  "> Being named among the UK's top 40 SMEs is a proud moment for the entire Onepoint team.\n" +
		  '> \n' +
		  '> **Shashin Shah, Founder & CEO.**\n' +
		  '> \n' +
		  '> **ONEPOINT**\n' +
		  '>\n' +
		  '> This sensational achievement reflects the principles that have shaped Onepoint for over two decades — continuous innovation, measurable impact for clients, and a sustained commitment to community.\n' +
		  '>\n' +
		  '> Innovation is a central component of the EB100 assessment and is one of the main reasons why Onepoint was selected.\n' +
		  '>\n' +
		  '> **From friction to smart workflow – an example of Onepoint’s innovation**\n' +
		  '>\n' +
		  '> Aerospace and Defence organisations operate under some of the most demanding compliance requirements. Legacy in infrastructure, fragmented data silos, large volumes of unstructured content, and manual compliance processes often limit the ability of organisations to act quickly. In addition, the urgency of modern conflict has drastically increased the need to reduce the time it takes to go from ‘the lab to theatre’.\n' +
		  '>\n' +
		  '> Onepoint saw the standards compliance problem differently. This led to the development of Onepoint ConvertWise™, an intelligent workflow accelerator that automates the compliance content preparation, conversion, and validation process, governed by humans.\n' +
		  '>\n' +
		  '> Onepoint ConvertWise™ delivers monumental efficiency gains for organisations under immense pressure to innovate and deliver faster.\n' +
		  '>\n' +
		  '> **SME innovation at scale**\n' +
		  '>\n' +
		  "> Onepoint partnered with Pennant International Group PLC to embed Onepoint ConvertWise™ into the services Pennant offers to the aerospace, defence and heavy industry sectors. The collaboration demonstrates Onepoint's capabilities and how an\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "SME can contribute fresh thinking and acceleration to one of the world's most established sectors.\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  '## Technology with purpose\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "Beyond growth and innovation, Onepoint continues to prioritise its mission to add value to society. The balance between commercial delivery and social contribution has been part of Onepoint's philosophy since its founding.\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  'The commitment has continued through sustained support for charitable organisations, programmes that create employment opportunities for the underprivileged, and investment in apprentices and interns entering the technology industry.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '**Shashin Shah, Founder & CEO of Onepoint**, commented, “Being named among the UK’s top 40 SMEs is a proud moment for the entire Onepoint team.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'It reflects a belief that has guided us from the beginning: that the true value of technology lies in bridging the gap between ambition and measurable outcomes.”\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '## About Onepoint\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Onepoint is an award-winning, architecture-led technology consultancy, headquartered in London. For over 20 years, we have been values-driven and committed to delivering enduring social and business value. We craft and manage impactful AI-powered, data-driven, enterprise-grade solutions for global clients. Find out more at [onepointltd.ai
			](http: //onepointltd.ai).\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '## About Onepoint ConvertWise™\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Onepoint ConvertWise™ simplifies the complex and resource-intensive process of converting legacy technical documentation. A smart workbench, ConvertWise automates the conversion into S1000D-compliant modular formats, significantly reducing time, cost, and complexity for industries like aerospace and defence. Find out more at [onepointltd.com/convertwise
			](http: //onepointltd.com/convertwise).\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '## Contact\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '**Suresh Sharma,**  \n' +
		  'Chief Customer Officer\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Email: suresh@onepointltd.com  \n' +
		  'Mobile: +44 7947 947 905  \n' +
		  '\n' +
