		reference_id: '7',
		content: 'Subject:\n' +
		  '- A message of gratitude and reflection\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Dear [Name
			],\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'As we come to the close of 2025, I want to take a moment to share a message of gratitude and reflection.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'This year marked a noteworthy landmark for Onepoint: 20 years of delivering real business value through technology, AI, and data-driven solutions to our clients around the world.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Onepoint started with a simple belief: a values-driven collection of technologists can help solve real pain points for stakeholders by bringing architecture-led innovation and unwavering focus on business outcomes. Two decades later, that philosophy remains unchanged, but the tools, opportunities, and challenges have certainly evolved.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Our year-long celebrations included a Gratitude Weekend at the serene Global Retreat Centre in Oxfordshire, England. The weekend was dedicated to reflecting on our journey, appreciating our community, and envisioning what’s ahead. You can read more about this and view the highlight video here: [LinkedIn link
			]\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Onepoint at 20: Reflecting, celebrating, and looking ahead\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Reflections from 2025\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Looking ahead to 2026\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "As we carry these reflections forward, I am also excited to share how our learning over the last 20 years has shaped Onepoint's next chapter.\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  'In 2026, our focus remains clear:\n' +
		  '- To craft AI, data, and automation solutions and tools that amplify human judgement, not replace it. (We call this Accelerated by Onepoint)\n' +
		  '- To advise business and technology leaders on how to get the most out of technical innovations to drive real business value. (We call this Woven by Onepoint)\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Thank you for being on the journey with us. Your trust and partnership have helped shape who we are today and who we continue to become.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '(GIF)\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Wishing you a reflective and regenerative close to 2025 and a hopeful, purposeful, and peaceful New Year.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'With warmest wishes,\n' +
		  'Shashin and the Onepoint family',
		file_path: '/var/graphrag/tennants/gil_fernandes/lightrag/onepoint_v3/input/01_New Content/Onepoint_s_20-year.txt',
		chunk_id: 'chunk-e9ab6fff1c3be843e5f5bdf69d8077bf',
