		reference_id: '12',
		content: 'Evaluation Warning: The document was created with Spire.Doc for Python.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "Hi, I'm Chris Wray, a Senior Adviser with Onepoint Consulting. To most clients that we speak with, AI isn't just a buzzword, it's an essential driver of real-world value, and they grapple with several crucial questions. How do you move from ambition to actual impact? How do you weave this powerful technology into the very fabric of your organisation in a way that's scalable, secure, and delivers measurable outcomes?\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  'At Onepoint, we believe the answer lies in a smarter approach. For over two decades, our enterprise heritage has helped leaders turn strategy into reality. We apply that same discipline to AI.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  `Our "Woven by Onepoint" proposition is our comprehensive consulting and delivery service. We work with you across the entire AI lifecycle from defining your strategy and architecture to building and scaling solutions that are designed for your unique constraints and goals. We help you weave AI into your organisation's DNA, creating measurable outcomes, not just feel-good experiments.\n` +
		  '\n' +
		  `But what if you need to get to value faster? That's where "Accelerated by Onepoint" comes in. We believe in borrowing what works, then tailoring it to fit your business. Our ecosystem of pre-built platforms, toolkits, frameworks, and methods are proven accelerators. They compress delivery time, reduce risk, and allow your teams to focus on differentiation, not reinvention. It's about getting from idea to impact (faster), (cheaper), and safer. To do this, we leverage what large language models truly excel at, moving far beyond generic chatbots.\n` +
		  '\n' +
		  'First, we use AI to build proprietary knowledge graphs from your trusted content, ingesting content types from technical documents to expert profiles. This creates a structured, interconnected knowledge asset, what we call a "Book of Knowledge" that understands the key concepts and relationships related to your specific use case.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "Then we deploy the most appropriate user interface. This can include a reverse chatbot experience. Instead of you asking all the questions, our AI advisors act like a senior consultant, asking you targeted diagnostic questions. This is our AI-driven inquiry logic at work, a guided conversation that uncovers your specific needs with precision. It's an...\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  'approach that extracts deep knowledge, matches complex patterns, and delivers personalised, high-impact solutions in a completely secure environment.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  `This all comes to life through the Onepoint AI Engine™, our foundational toolkit for custom AI solutions. For example, our D-Well smart advisor uses this engine to ask you questions about your data ecosystem and provides practical guidance on everything from governance to quality. Another, our "Expert Matcher," uses a knowledge graph built from investment delivers value again and individuals' profiles to help you find the right internal expert for a specific challenge in minutes.\n` +
		  '\n' +
		  'To build these solutions rapidly, we use our toolkits. These are ready-to-use building blocks like our library of AI connectors for the Boomi platform or the core components of our AI engine. These toolkits provide the essential plumbing, allowing us to construct and deploy sophisticated AI agents and workflows without starting from scratch every time.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Our work is guided by our frameworks. These are our curated bodies of Analytics Body of Knowledge, codifying decades of expert insights into a single comprehensive guide. These frameworks ensure our solutions are grounded in proven industry best practices for consistency and scalability. We build custom bodies of knowledge for our clients in their domain, from specifications that ship to hundreds of articles and videos on innovation.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'And we deliver this value through our proven methods. If you need to validate an idea quickly, our Value Path method delivers a proof of value with measurable outcomes in just four to six weeks. For large-scale business-critical projects, our End-to-End Rapid Value method provides the disciplined framework to turn an ambitious vision into enterprise-grade reality.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'The real power of our approach is that the solutions we build are not single-purpose. They are archetypes. The same design that powers our RES AI smart advisor for responsible AI guidance could be adapted to create a legal triage assistant. A solution built to find the right expert in a law firm can be reconfigured to help customers find the right expert.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'right product in a complex portfolio. This adaptability means your aim across multiple parts of your business.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "Stop experimenting with AI and start embedding it with confidence. Whether you're ready to define your strategy or want to prove the value of a specific use case, the first step is a conversation.\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  "Let's build what's next together. Book a discovery call with one of our experts today. Thank you for listening.",
