		  'Onepoint demonstrates AI-driven enterprise innovation at Boomi World 2025, Dallas\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'London, United Kingdom—xx May 2025—Onepoint, an award-winning, architecture-led boutique technology consultancy, announced its AI ecosystem for the Boomi platform at Boomi World 2025, held in Dallas. The company showcased how its pre-made connectors, workflows, and agents are helping global enterprises automate business processes, enable hyper productivity, and deliver measurable business impact.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'During a session titled "Discovering Boomi Partner AI Agents", Onepoint demonstrated how its AI Ecosystem for Boomi is being used across industries to drive automation, enhance data quality, and improve operational agility. The solution suite currently consists of circa 40 components for the Boomi platform.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '“Our AI-powered connectors, workflows, and agents extend the capabilities of Boomi’s platform, enabling enterprises to increase innovation and reduce time-to-value while maintaining architectural integrity,” said Rafiq Rajabally, Business Developer at Onepoint.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'The presentation demonstrated real-world scenarios including:\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- **Customer service transformation**: Resolving high call centre traffic and social media escalations through AI-driven intelligent triage and escalation workflows.\n' +
		  '  \n' +
		  '- **Operational data integration**: Seamlessly merging multi-source travel booking data to deliver standardised reporting and risk insights.\n' +
		  '  \n' +
		  '- **Supply chain automation**: Proactively forecasting and resolving inventory risks.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Each scenario demonstrated how Onepoint’s bespoke agents leverage Boomi’s platform to deliver rapid, repeatable, and secure agentic AI solutions — now available via the Boomi Marketplace.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '**Presentation material:**\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'The presentation slides and photographs from the event are available on Onepoint’s website at [www.onepointltd.com/onepoint-at-boomi-world-2025-assets
			].\n' +
