		  '# Intelligent procurement orchestration\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Generative AI, cloud, and RPA-enabled solutions to streamline source-to-pay processes, automate document handling, contracts, and supplier analysis.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Streamlining source-to-pay processes is a perennial challenge, often hampered by siloed systems, manual document handling, and inconsistent data. While traditional automation can address isolated tasks, it often struggles to orchestrate the complex, end-to-end workflows and handle the unstructured data inherent in contracts and supplier communications.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'This domain is highly relevant to our core expertise in integration and advanced automation. Our strong partnership with Boomi, combined with our proven experience in RPA and cloud delivery, positions us as a leading partner for procurement transformation.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "Onepoint's expertise lies in architecting and delivering intelligent orchestration platforms that solve complex challenges. As the Boomi EMEA Teaming Systems Integrator Partner of the Year 2023, our leadership in integration is the foundation for unifying disparate systems.\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  'With our client-centric innovation focus, we extended the capabilities of the Boomi platform with our Onepoint AI Ecosystem™ for Boomi, using agentic AI to manage complex workflows.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Our proven experience in RPA has delivered 95% digitisation and automation for clients. We leverage our Onepoint AI Engine to build custom Generative AI agents for advanced document and contract analysis.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'We partner with innovation leaders like Emagia, whose AI-powered platform for Autonomous Finance excels in streamlining order-to-cash and procure-to-pay processes. This combination of our orchestration expertise and ability to integrate specialised automation solutions allows us to deliver a complete solution that fits your exact needs.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Three key capabilities of Onepoint that are particularly relevant to generative AI, cloud, and RPA-enabled solutions to streamline source-to-pay processes, automate document handling, contracts, and supplier analysis.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '## Generative AI and automation\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Onepoint is at the forefront of leveraging AI for enterprise automation:\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- **Agentic AI Ecosystem** – We have launched the Onepoint AI Ecosystem for Boomi, which delivers circa 40 agentic components to accelerate enterprise automation. This technology is designed for the design, governance, and orchestration of AI agents at scale, which is key to orchestrating complex source-to-pay workflows and automated analysis.\n' +
		  '  \n' +
		  '- **Boomi partnership** – We were recognised as the Boomi EMEA Teaming Systems Integrator Partner of the Year 2023. We are pushing harder on our Boomi relationship and view Boomi as a key platform for AI-driven automation. Our strategic goal is to establish market leadership in agentic AI implementations by leveraging our Boomi expertise.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- **Onepoint Smart Enterprise Automation™ (RPA and process automation)** – We are actively involved in RPA and are exploring the full potential of AI in this domain. We have experience in automating critical finance workflows for clients, achieving 95% digitisation and automation of each workflow, and saving over 200 person-hours per month. This work specifically involved minimising human errors by automating repetitive, rule-based tasks such as data entry, invoice processing, and reconciliation. These capabilities are directly applicable to streamlining source-to-pay processes.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '## Seamless source-to-pay integration and data management\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Our methodology and platform expertise directly support integrating disparate procurement and finance systems:\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "- **Integration and MDM**: We leverage the Boomi Integration Platform as a Service (iPaaS) for complex integration and Master Data Management (MDM). For one client (anonymised as 'SolarCo'), we set up data → \n" +
		  '\n' +
		  'Seamless source-to-pay integration and data management (continued)\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- foundations that enabled seamless communication across over 20 applications (including SAP S4Hana, Procurement, and Finance) to achieve operational efficiency, enhanced data quality, and scalability. This experience is highly relevant to unifying source-to-pay processes.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- Document and contract analysis — Our focus on Generative AI and Natural language processing (NLP) can be leveraged to automate document handling, contract analysis, and supplier analysis—by building custom AI agents on the Onepoint AI Engine.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Cloud and architecture foundation\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Onepoint’s solutions are built on resilient, scalable cloud architectures:\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- Cloud platform expertise — We have deep expertise in cloud platforms, particularly with Microsoft Azure, which is the leading cloud platform preferred by our customers. We are experienced in architecting and delivering enterprise-grade solutions on Microsoft Azure, AWS, and Google Cloud.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Enterprise-grade delivery — As a boutique consultancy that delivers enterprise-grade solutions, we prioritise architecting for outcomes. This ensures that any Procurement Orchestration Platform we design is scalable, secure, and compliant with your corporate requirements.\n' +
