		  '\n' +
		  'From strategy to scale, weave AI into your organisation with confidence.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  "AI is no longer optional — it's essential. But weaving AI into the fabric of your organisation requires more than just tools or pilots. It demands a clear strategy, robust architecture, and a proven approach to scaling solutions that deliver real business value.\n" +
		  '\n' +
		  'Woven by Onepoint is our umbrella proposition for AI consulting and delivery. From early-stage ideas to enterprise-grade AI solutions, we help you weave AI into your organisation’s DNA — creating measurable outcomes, not just experiments.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '---\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '**Built on five key differentiators**\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '1. Our architecture heritage\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Two decades of enterprise architecture practice results in interoperable, scalable, secure solutions designed for real constraints. Pilots become platforms, not throwaways.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '1. Trusted advisors to senior leaders  \n' +
		  'Independent, experience-led counsel from boardroom to backlog, turning strategy into funded roadmaps and keeping delivery accountable—trusted by organisations like Flight Centre, Lightsource bp, Meggitt, and Moto Hospitality.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '2. Outcome-focused  \n' +
		  'We prioritise measurable business value over hype. We bring a business consultancy’s mindset of value creation with a technology specialist’s ability to weave technical innovation that realises business opportunities.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '3. Proven methods and toolkits  \n' +
		  'Reusable frameworks, playbooks, and accelerators cut time-to-value and leave assets your teams can reuse—speed up delivery, standardise good practice across teams, and create assets you can lift-and-shift to the next project.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '4. Blend of skills and capabilities  \n' +
		  'Onshore and offshore cross-functional teams (strategy, product, architecture, data/AI, engineering, DevOps) co-create with you, shipping value while upskilling your people.\n' +
		  ' \n' +
