		  'Frequently asked questions\n' +
		  '# What is Woven by Onepoint?\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Woven by Onepoint is our comprehensive AI consulting and delivery proposition. It helps organisations weave AI into their business, from strategy and architecture to proofs-of-value, scaling, and ongoing management. We focus on delivering measurable outcomes by combining our architecture expertise, trusted advisory experience, and proven methods.\n' +
		  '\n' +
