		  '- **AI Build** — Develop tailored AI solutions that integrate with your business.\n' +
		  '- **AI Scaling** — Operationalise and scale AI across teams, regions, and use cases.\n' +
		  '- **AI Managed** — Ensure ongoing performance, governance, and continuous improvement.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '## How does Woven by Onepoint differentiate from other AI consulting services?\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Woven by Onepoint stands out because of our:\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- **Architecture heritage**: 20 years of experience designing enterprise-grade systems.\n' +
