		  '- **Proven methods**: Frameworks, toolkits, and accelerators that reduce risk and accelerate time-to-value.\n' +
		  '- **Outcome focus**: We prioritise measurable business value over hype.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '## Can you help us scale AI beyond pilots?\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Yes. Scaling AI is a core part of Woven by Onepoint. We help you move from isolated proofs-of-value to enterprise-grade AI solutions by:\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- Designing scalable architectures.\n' +
		  '- Embedding governance and compliance.\n' +
		  '- Creating reusable patterns and playbooks.\n' +
		  '- Supporting adoption across teams and regions.\n' +
		  'How fast can we see results?\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'With our proven methods and accelerators, we can deliver a working proof-of-value in as little as 4–6 weeks. This includes a technical proof-of-concept and a use case / business proof-of-value, with measurable outcomes, reusable components, and a clear path to scale.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'What industries does Woven by Onepoint support?\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'We work across a wide range of industries, including:\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- Financial services\n' +
		  '- Travel, retail, and hospitality\n' +
		  '- Energy and utilities\n' +
		  '- Manufacturing and aerospace\n' +
		  '- Public sector and regulated industries\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Our approach is tailored to your industry’s specific challenges, compliance requirements, and opportunities.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'How do you ensure AI solutions are compliant and explainable?\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Governance and explainability are built into every stage of our process. We:\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- Align solutions to your policies, standards, and risk appetite.\n' +
		  '- Use explainable AI techniques to provide transparent, auditable outputs.\n' +
		  '- Embed compliance controls for regulated industries.\n' +
		  '- Provide documentation and training to ensure ongoing accountability.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Can you customise your approach to our organisation?\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'Absolutely. While we use proven frameworks and accelerators to speed up delivery, everything we do is tailored to your organisation’s goals, data, policies, and systems. We work closely with your teams to ensure the solution fits your uniqueness.\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  'What’s the difference between Woven by Onepoint and Accelerated by Onepoint?\n' +
		  '\n' +
		  '- Woven by Onepoint focuses on consulting and delivery—helping you weave AI into your organisation through strategy, architecture, proofs-of-value, scaling, and management.\n' +
		  '\n' +
